This workspace contains multiple repositories:

- `api`: Open Learning Tools API package
- `auth-client`: OpenBase auth and django-allauth React client
- `api-core`: Open Learning Tools Django API core runtime
- `ui`: Shared OpenBase React UI package
- `web`: Open Learning Tools React web frontend
- `deploy`: OpenBase deployment CLI and reusable Terraform app stack
